{"tid":1118091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"他們曾說過……","createTime":"2019-04-21T07:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T07:18:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"49d08ae51c5f449190fa9c1868688799197b2250","tid":1118091,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T07:18:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190421/20660768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190421%2F20660768&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RLY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=26f23f8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190421%2F20660768&h=81bec08a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190421/20660768</a><br />\n<br />\n他們曾說過&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190421/large/a0804a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190421%2Flarge%2Fa0804a.gif&h=ea67cedd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左至右：倪匡、徐克、黃霑及蔡瀾當年於亞視節目《今夜不設防》發表意見。<br />\n<br />\n「𠵱家係表現人性最好嘅時候，係人性醜惡同人性美好決鬥嘅時候。香港人𠵱家個個都企喺光明一面，問題係點樣堅持落去，攞香港建造成中國最後一個民主嘅堡壘、自由嘅堡壘。香港人絕對可以做到呢一件事，只要無孔不入、各盡所能，一定可以做到。」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;小說家倪匡在1989年六四後於亞視節目《今夜不設防》發表意見  <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：難忘大雨停電漆黑高呼<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n填詞人周禮茂 深信終可平反<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n蘋人誌：爸爸自焚換自由 女兒學着不哭泣－鄭竹梅<br />\n<br />\n難忘大雨停電漆黑高呼<br />\n填詞人周禮茂 深信終可平反<br />\n告誡中共「人民不會忘記」90後樂隊重編《自由花》"}]}